
         
         <p>I just published a new project called <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">spacious-padding</code>.  This is yet
another package of mine for GNU Emacs.  It increases the padding or
spacing of frames and windows on demand.</p>

<p>The idea with this package is to provide the means to easily toggle
between terse and spacious views, depending on the userâ€™s needs.</p>

<p>Below are a couple of pictures to show what I mean.</p>

