<h2>Coming soon</h2>

<p>There will be no widely available GNU ELPA package for the first days
of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">spacious-padding</code>.  Only those who track the GNU ELPA-devel
archive or pull directly from source can get it right now.  I want to
test this for a while longer before tagging version <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0.1.0</code>.  Expect
the formal release some time next week.</p>

<p>Inspiration for this package comes from <a href="https://github.com/rougier">Nicolas Rougierâ€™s impressive
designs</a> and <a href="https://github.com/minad/org-modern">Daniel Mendlerâ€™s
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">org-modern</code> package</a>.</p>

